COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent
v.
Kaitlyn N. WOLFEL, Petitioner No. 141 WAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. April 10, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM

AND NOW, this 10 th day of April, 2019, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is GRANTED. The issue, as stated by Petitioner is:

Whether the Superior Court of Pennsylvania disregarded the controlling authority of Birchfield v. North Dakota, ___ U.S. ___, 136 S.Ct. 2160 , 195 L.Ed.2d 560 (2016), by reversing the trial court's decision suppressing the results of the testing of Petitioner's blood.
